{
  "2275010": {
    "name": "Ardent Wilds",
    "steam_appid": 2275010,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275010/extras/15b6932ea6f0d67fb963778b836fae82.avif?t=1754647729\" width=618 height=346 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>你在一处古老的炽热保护机构遗址中苏醒</strong>，该遗址早已被遗弃且藤蔓丛生。以太枢纽——曾是星球防御的核心——如今沉寂无声。没有它，埃尔德兰的腐化便无拘无束地蔓延，玷污大地并吞噬其魔力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>打造强力装备</strong>，尝试<strong>无限法术组合</strong>，释放你的创造力，施展<strong>永久改变地形</strong>的法术。利用以太网络的力量，<strong>开启全新能力</strong>，开辟属于你自己的未来之路。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>与扭曲生物战斗，挑战传奇首领，揭开古老秘密。</strong>无论你是独自勇闯未知，还是与好友协作，每一次冒险都由你主宰。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275010/extras/ad4bfe2be96812ea2714721df375375e.webp?t=1754647729\" width=618 height=44 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275010/extras/15dc4b7bc2007c86af747067dead56c2.poster.avif?t=1754647729\" width=628 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275010/extras/15dc4b7bc2007c86af747067dead56c2.webm?t=1754647729\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275010/extras/15dc4b7bc2007c86af747067dead56c2.mp4?t=1754647729\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>挖掘隧道、雕刻精美雕像或用仅有的铲子和决心夷平整座山脉</strong>。法术与技能以动态方式塑造地形，炸弹和火焰冲击留下炙热弹坑，而冰霜之书则让你在自制的冰桥上穿越峡谷。如果你曾梦想掌控元素，这里正是你的游乐场。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275010/extras/ad4bfe2be96812ea2714721df375375e.webp?t=1754647729\" width=618 height=44 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275010/extras/d2400792b66c7f3a843c80547e10da39.poster.avif?t=1754647729\" width=628 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275010/extras/d2400792b66c7f3a843c80547e10da39.webm?t=1754647729\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275010/extras/d2400792b66c7f3a843c80547e10da39.mp4?t=1754647729\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索荒野，通过激活古老的以太设施来恢复其防御——每个设施都能解锁全新升级和路径。乘着以太光束穿越大地，策略性地激活这座庞大的物理天赋树中的技能。你能否掌握其全部潜能？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275010/extras/ad4bfe2be96812ea2714721df375375e.webp?t=1754647729\" width=618 height=44 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275010/extras/c82f2334a299ab71632929f4ae0ab7d2.poster.avif?t=1754647729\" width=628 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275010/extras/c82f2334a299ab71632929f4ae0ab7d2.webm?t=1754647729\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275010/extras/c82f2334a299ab71632929f4ae0ab7d2.mp4?t=1754647729\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集材料以建造并升级你的基地。在专用工作站<strong>打造强力护甲与武器</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >利用各式家具和装饰品打造梦想中的奇幻家园，或通过<strong>种植作物</strong>、<strong>烹饪美味佳肴</strong>和<strong>酿造强效药剂</strong>来提升你的旅程，为战斗助力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275010/extras/ad4bfe2be96812ea2714721df375375e.webp?t=1754647729\" width=618 height=44 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275010/extras/e3f17eb047140d7ea7781abf4a051392.poster.avif?t=1754647729\" width=628 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275010/extras/e3f17eb047140d7ea7781abf4a051392.webm?t=1754647729\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275010/extras/e3f17eb047140d7ea7781abf4a051392.mp4?t=1754647729\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >深入探索洞穴和古老地下堡垒，每个角落都潜伏着危险。在这些黑暗迷宫般的洞窟中，你将遇到致命陷阱、凶猛敌人以及等待揭晓的秘密。但风险总会带来回报——珍贵战利品、稀有材料和强力神器就埋藏其中，等待足够勇敢的人去争取。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275010/extras/ad4bfe2be96812ea2714721df375375e.webp?t=1754647729\" width=618 height=44 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275010/extras/5e0b8968eefd18f108ba4cca4edc3d31.poster.avif?t=1754647729\" width=628 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275010/extras/5e0b8968eefd18f108ba4cca4edc3d31.webm?t=1754647729\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275010/extras/5e0b8968eefd18f108ba4cca4edc3d31.mp4?t=1754647729\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在你的制作站上打造强力护甲与武器，利用旅途中收集的材料。或者，一些最佳装备可从被击败的敌人身上获得。无论你是打造还是征服，每件装备都将增强你的实力，为更大挑战做好准备。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275010/extras/ad4bfe2be96812ea2714721df375375e.webp?t=1754647729\" width=618 height=44 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275010/extras/6c79c82a8baa0293f47b5002ea2837a3.poster.avif?t=1754647729\" width=628 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275010/extras/6c79c82a8baa0293f47b5002ea2837a3.webm?t=1754647729\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275010/extras/6c79c82a8baa0293f47b5002ea2837a3.mp4?t=1754647729\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >准备迎战史诗级首领，在激烈且令人心跳加速的战斗中检验你的技巧与策略。你必须携带最强装备、技能与团队协作，才能一战告捷。胜利将带来丰厚奖励——击败这些强大对手，你将获得传说级战利品、稀有物品以及大幅提升实力的强力武器。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275010/extras/ad4bfe2be96812ea2714721df375375e.webp?t=1754647729\" width=618 height=44 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275010/extras/1c8253ef73d8fb246f47ddf97233c851.poster.avif?t=1754647729\" width=628 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275010/extras/1c8253ef73d8fb246f47ddf97233c851.webm?t=1754647729\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275010/extras/1c8253ef73d8fb246f47ddf97233c851.mp4?t=1754647729\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Ardent Wilds》提供最多6人在线合作模式，让你与好友共同探索并征服。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >（*玩家人数可超出6人，但游戏平衡不适用于更大团队。）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275010/extras/ad4bfe2be96812ea2714721df375375e.webp?t=1754647729\" width=618 height=44 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >额外特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >广泛的模组支持：所有游戏对象、生物、技能及战斗效果均可通过我们的 Lua API 进行编程。需要示例吗？所有现有内容的脚本均随游戏附带，且均可供你查看和修改。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过多种发型、胡须、颜色及其他自定义选项来定制你的英雄。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >没有网络？没问题！游戏可通过局域网 (LAN) 以及 Steam 进行多人游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p></li></ul>",
